    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>CCMS GLT 2342 Screen to quickly create a consignee (generalised to other types of agents) and a cash-only debtor together,
when a new cash payment agent arrives to pay for cargo.  Also quickly find an existing consignee by name.
(Gulftainer Umm Qasr have a number of consignees with very similiar names)</text>
